list.name: Default
list.comment: - play cursor removed when stop - zoom cursor can be moved with left and right arrow keys - when recording show only oscillogram and previous config restored when stop (also mouse disabled when stop) - histogram put horizontally - stop if zoom cursor moved when playing - zoom cursor overall fixes in both oscillogram and spectrogram - new default (5 sec silence at 44100 Hz) signal opened when the application starts - open does not set default setings, uses what's set in the settings tree - settings parameter tree is no longer fixed height
